headline: 3 Consumer Stocks in Hot Water
summary: Consumer staples are considered safe havens in turbulent markets due to their inelastic demand profiles. But recently, the industry has failed to do its job as it shed 9.5% over the past six months. This drop was especially discouraging since the S&P 500 held steady.
